quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  9,94,YaÂŽtezirune ilykĂŒm iza racaÂŽtĂŒm ileyhim kul la taÂŽteziru len nĂŒÂŽmine lekĂŒm kad nebbeenellahĂŒ min ahbarikĂŒm ve se yerallahĂŒ amelekĂŒm ve rasulĂŒhu sĂŒmme tĂŒraddune ila alimil Äaybi veĆ Ćehadeti fe yĂŒnebbiĂŒkĂŒm bi ma kĂŒntĂŒm taÂŽmelun
  9,95,Se yahlifune billahi lekĂŒm izenkalebtĂŒm ileyhim li tuÂŽridu anhĂŒm fe aÂŽridu anhĂŒm innehĂŒm ricsĂŒv ve meÂŽvahĂŒm cehennem cezaem bi ma kanu yeksibun
  9,96,Yahlifune lekĂŒm li terdav anhĂŒm fe in terdav anhĂŒm fe innellahe la yerda anil kavmil fasikÄ±yn
  9,97,El aÂŽrabĂŒ eĆeddĂŒ kĂŒfrav ve nifakav ve ecderu ella yaÂŽlemu hudude ma enzelellahĂŒ ala rasulih vallahĂŒ alÄ±mĂŒn hakÄ±m
  9,98,Ve minel aÂŽrabi mey yettehÄ±zĂŒ ma yĂŒnfiku maÄramev ve yeterabbesu bikĂŒmĂŒd devair aleyhim dairatĂŒs sevÂŽ vallahĂŒ semÄ±un alÄ±m
  9,99,Ve minel aÂŽrabi mey yĂŒÂŽminĂŒ billahi vel yevmil ahÄ±ri ve yettehÄ±zĂŒ ma yĂŒnfiku kurubatin Ä±ndellahi ve salevatir rasul ela inneha kurbetĂŒl lehĂŒm se yĂŒdhÄ±lĂŒhĂŒmĂŒllahĂŒ fÄ± rahmetih innellahe Äafurur rahÄ±ym